{
  "texts": [
    "We generate one use case for each candidate tool, resulting in a total of 17 use cases.",
    "To provide a further analysis of the generated user cases, we classified each user case based on the accessibility of the external content.",
    "Cases where the external content is harder to access present more challenges for attackers to inject malicious instructions.",
    "For instance, a shared note in Evernote, typically accessible only to a select group, is more difficult to access than a widely available Amazon product review.",
    "We used GPT-4 to classify the level of difficulty and provide the results with several examples in Appendix A."
  ]
}